Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 07 of Mamma MRI
When I select the radio button 'Enlarged lymph nodes with fatty hilum'
Then checkbox 'Right' is enabled
And checkbox 'Left' is enabled
When I check 'Right' checkbox
Then 'Max. short axis diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Level I: below the lower edge of the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level II: underneath/posterior the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level III: above/medial the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox is enabled
When I check 'Left' checkbox
Then 'Max. short axis diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Level I: below the lower edge of the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level II: underneath/posterior the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level III: above/medial the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox is enabled
When I enter '20' in 'Max. short axis diameter' input field of 'Right'
And I check 'Level I: below the lower edge of the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox in 'Right'
And I check 'Level II: underneath/posterior the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox in 'Right'
And I check 'Level III: above/medial the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox in 'Right'
And I enter '10' in 'Max. short axis diameter' input field of 'Right'
And I check 'Level I: below the lower edge of the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox in 'Right'
And I check 'Level II: underneath/posterior the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox in 'Right'
And I check 'Level III: above/medial the pectoralis minor muscle' checkbox in 'Right'
And I click on 'Next page' button
Then I'm redirected to Page 08 of Mamma MRI
